This project is developed to learn the spring core and spring MVC. 
This project is simple Model (i.e. Player, Reservation and SportType), View (Reservation Service) and Controller (FormController, 
queryController) representation.
This project get the playername, sport date, player number and sport type from the user.
Shows the timetable and find the particular sport or player from the uploaded data.

To Start the tomcat server:

    go to windows ->
    select show view ->
    select server. i. select apache tomcat and give the tomcat directory path.
